{"tid":217732,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣布 我同會員阿古路唔再係朋友😃","createTime":"2017-04-26T04:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T07:42:23.000Z","uid":35341,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16c7f739027da05c8a69c2070d0055fe87c31104","tid":217732,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:00:38.000Z","msg":"😃"},{"pid":"cef8e6bd624c43a5d6e17f6f6dc4c007eeb070a1","tid":217732,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:01:28.000Z","msg":"原因 佢無證據情況下抵毀楊采妮"},{"pid":"28dadba0328172920e0cbe26c58867b7638ae6b1","tid":217732,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:03:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原因 佢無證據情況下抵毀楊采妮</blockquote><br />\ng<br />\n是其是<br />\n非其非"},{"pid":"372599b761827a888aec26fd61ca1de237599c26","tid":217732,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:05:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原因 佢無證據情況下抵毀楊采妮</blockquote><br />\ng<br />\n是其是<br />\n非其非</blockquote><br />\n近日本討論區出現一系列之「G」主題，發現其中有為數不少之會員，並無充份證據，甚至連對話記錄也沒有，單憑一張相片便標籤女星為「臭G」。我們團隊希望會員在對他人作出這種嚴重指控前審慎思考理據，小心求証，以避免有人被無辜牽連。<br />\n<br />\n本討論區著重言論自由，若內容有充足理據支持，我們絕不會無故刪除有關內容。但我們也不希望當中有無辜人仕在無充份証明下遭受如此嚴重的指控，經管理團隊商議後，已於辦工時間立即進行處理並決定刪除相關討論。我們團隊日後也會致力維持本討論區之良好討論氣氛及風氣。"},{"pid":"dd938a6411f1916ee081823206cb79cf1fc0faf7","tid":217732,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:07:21.000Z","msg":"今後各行各路"},{"pid":"c3eeb99f0dbe783091b07a88bd22933ff3bac0cc","tid":217732,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:08:47.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/208548/page/3?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/208548/page/3?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"64df9f8df16024af3f5d1c87daffe04b86ee928f","tid":217732,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:23:12.000Z","msg":"是其是非其非😢"},{"pid":"00bd75bd469f3870